: Automatic Door Opener with Face Detection
Problem Statement:
Traditional door locks are prone to security risks and require
physical interaction.
Objective:
Build a smart access system that uses facial recognition to
automatically unlock doors.
Requirements:
Raspberry Pi (or laptop for testing)
USB Camera
OpenCV (Python) for face detection
Servo Motor
Jumper wires, battery pack
Expected Outcome:
A face-based automatic door opener—enhancing security and
offering a hands-free access solution.

